---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  lang="en"
  active="support"
  title="Support | Food Label Detective"
  description="Feedback, bug reports, and additive data correction suggestions for Food Label Detective."
  alternateUrl="/app/tr/support/"
>
  <main class="site-shell policy-hero policy-content">
    <span class="eyebrow">Support</span>
    <h1>Let’s make one more label easier to understand.</h1>
    <p class="lede">You can send bug reports, data correction suggestions, translation notes, or feedback about the app experience.</p>

    <div class="grid-2">
      <article class="card"><span class="icon">✉</span><strong>Email</strong><p><a href="mailto:mehmetbkm@gmail.com">mehmetbkm@gmail.com</a></p></article>
      <article class="card"><span class="icon">↻</span><strong>Data corrections</strong><p>You may suggest corrections for an additive description, halal status, risk level, or warning note.</p></article>
    </div>

    <h2>When sending feedback</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Include the relevant E-code or additive name.</li>
      <li>If it relates to a product label, quote the wording from the package.</li>
      <li>If you report an OCR issue, briefly mention lighting, angle, or the unreadable area.</li>
      <li>The app does not provide medical assessment.</li>
    </ul>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
